data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on a picturesque 1-acre lot, where the tranquility of nature meets modern comfort. This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of elegance and functionality. Enjoy lazy afternoons on the covered front porch, complete with a swing and and plenty of space for decorative plants and entertaining. Step inside to discover a cozy family room featuring a gas fireplace with beautiful flooring throughout. The home boasts a recently renovated kitchen and custom master bathroom with a lavish shower, providing a spa-like retreat within the comfort of your own space. Ascend the stairs to reveal an additional loft space, perfect for a home office, playroom, or cozy reading nook. The possibilities are endless in this versatile area, offering an extra dimension to the already generous living space. As you make your way outdoors, be captivated by the expansive deck overlooking the private backyard—a perfect setting for entertaining guests, enjoying morning coffee, or simply unwinding after a long day. For those with a green thumb or a desire for sustainable living, the property features plenty of space for gardening and a charming chicken coop, inviting you to embrace a farm-to-table lifestyle right at home. Convenience is key, and this home delivers. Located just minutes from town and the ease of access to Interstate 75, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of rural serenity and urban convenience. Embrace the best of both worlds in this meticulously crafted residence—your haven in the heart of nature, just a stone's throw from city amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this enchanting property your own. 30 year roof installed in 2017 — both hvac systems replaced in 2019 — water heater replaced in 2021 — home converted to city water in 2021. Welcome home!
